.RS 4
.TP 24
.BR copy_point
copy a point struct
.TP
.BR move_around_cyl
Move a point on the surface of a cylinder in an arbitrary direction
.TP
.BR set_point_cyl
Set the values of a "point" struct
.TP
.BR set_point_sph
Set the values of a "point" struct
.TP
.BR set_point_xyz
Set the values of a "point" struct
.RE
.PP
.I Pulsars
.RS 4
.TP 24
.BR create_pulsar
